column5: was going to head down to the lake o tribs tommorow .....is it worth the trip? we got some rain up here in caledon and i heard they got alot in barrie....but dont know about east of toronto? As long as there are fish im happy  please respond as im going in the morning lol  peace  mike
Cant say for sure....lots of rain east of Toronto...tribs are likely to be chocolate milk!  Good luck!
i think i may give it a try this afternoon or tommorrow morning...... a little to late for a heads up
